727706f-a.title: Queens: Queens Boulevard - Cornish Avenue
727706f-a.text:
Queens Boulevard, north side, between Cornish and
Barnwell Avenues, showing an old house, where puppies are
sold. This property was at one time owned by G.G. Andrews.
P. L. Sperr  June 7, 1927
